ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有一齊過，但都係分左手<br />\n我知道佢都好鍾意我，但係天意弄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好掛住佢</blockquote><br />\n或者可以咁諗 曾經一齊有段開心既經歷 有個咁既人出現 都係種幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626abe4871e752c1e99948486c736a961ba48b7e","tid":205342,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中學時期唔夠疆追人</blockquote><br />\n而家仲鍾意緊果個人？</blockquote><br />\n都過左7 年 冇啦而家冇曬feel 啦<br />\n<br />\n睇返呢個post 先諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人生或者就係有D人你以為忘記左但其實只係放響心更深處<br />\n<br />\n巴打加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4903aeb157305864d9c66964de3b43e4b1af282","tid":205342,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T18:09:00.000Z","msg":"冇好好讀書"},{"pid":"f245ba08a4cb07e081466fd403bafe9e8724ce1b","tid":205342,"uid":71422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T18:11:42.000Z","msg":"有過一個好愛好愛我既人，我唔識珍惜之餘仲傷害左佢。<br />\n分手一個月都無，佢就唔再係到。<br />\n當一個人既時候，真係好多好多好多後悔。<br />\n內疚，亦係我依一年黎陪住我既最好朋友。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}